						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">65024U wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Also, another question, what happens if 2 sprites overlap?</div><br />The one that appears first in the display list is in front. For example, the sprite at $08-$0B in OAM would show on top of the sprite at $24-$27.<br /><br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">And what about 0 bits, they don't get "placed" do they?</div>
<br />Color 0 is transparent. A sprite pixel whose color is 0 has the color of whatever is behind it: either background or another sprite.</div>

