						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">65024U wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">How many cycles does VBlank last anyway?</div>
<br />20 scanlines, which is about 2273 CPU cycles. You really do want to be finished with all PPU operations when that time runs out, which is why you shouldn't waste it with game logic.</div>

